{"tid":378953,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"戴過帽/因為第二個而飛你嘅巴絲 你地係點復原？","createTime":"2017-08-29T01:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T05:40:19.000Z","uid":36131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c31270b6d3bc6dd155f32a9b4d6d3b6bffdf252f","tid":378953,"uid":36131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T01:00:31.000Z","msg":"Ex 俾過帽你戴或者明個佢係因為鍾意左第二個先飛你嘅朋友<br />\n你地做過咩 點調節心態去等自己好番？<br />\n有冇試過唱開佢/復仇嘅經驗？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c71b5413ff049b0789fa9e4a0f508144acc06a","tid":378953,"uid":6294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T01:58:19.000Z","msg":"仲細咩 復仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認真答你 最緊要唔好迫自己祝福佢<br />\n呢啲仆街係唔配有人祝福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦都唔洗求你 唔洗係Facebook叫春<br />\n唯有好好過自己既日子<br />\n等佢他朝一日無意中知道你既近況個陣<br />\n知道你過得好撚精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8558768f70cacdcb33dc6d2cd16fbb69b85f6325","tid":378953,"uid":72688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T02:00:54.000Z","msg":"當叫免費雞屌過閪就算"},{"pid":"5fa6842e4dcf49e6220a360695bed9b18f436794","tid":378953,"uid":9792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T02:01:39.000Z","msg":"好返唔到<br />\n其實仲好想佢返黎..."},{"pid":"ca4a8029b96d521462e6f7d90c37e446133a05e5","tid":378953,"uid":129033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T02:05:10.000Z","msg":"唔會想報仇啦 但會好想作賤自己 因為失去左自信 其實如果建立返自信 過自己既生活 要去證明自己既價值 你有能力活得俾佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef10b191b1ebe03db0bdd1844e6eed33faf7c8d","tid":378953,"uid":52875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"時間耐左，就唔會再掛住ex<br />\n<br />\n但下次拍拖會驚再綠多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點都有d心理陰影<br />\n唯有同自己講&ldquo;上一個呃你，唔代表下一個呃你